column1: Table A3: Current Price (smoothed) GVA (B) per hour worked (£); Local Authority District,  2004 - 2022
Including UK figures for comparison purposes
Note 1: Data are current price; ie, data are not adjusted for inflation.
Note 2: Data are smoothed using a weighted 5-year moving average
Note 3: The GVA for Extra-Regio comprises compensation of employees and gross operating surplus which cannot be assigned to regions.
